name: Listened to Feldman’s ‘Freaks List’ 2023 + ACC Preview with Manny Navarro

content.html:
It’s that time of year again! Hopefully, everyone circled Freaks List Day on their calendars! The guys dig into Bruce’s annual Freaks List, and discuss overarching topics like; why is there a true Freshman leading the list? The Big Ten has some dudes, and how technology has evolved the way we view athletic specimens. Later, The Athletic’s Manny Navarro joins the podcast to discuss the ACC. Who is the conference’s dark horse? Lastly, we answer your mailbag questions!
